CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1957, pg. A17 reads: "Masters Of Ceremoines [sic]...Dr. M.R. Hadley of McKeesport escorts Mrs. Toki Schalk Johnson to the stage where they shared emcee honors at the AKA Cotillion."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Dr. M.R. Hadley and Toki Schalk Johnson, posed in Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Alpha Kappa Alpha 1957 Cotillion
